content.rendered:
With its unique frame and detail on the seat & backrest, the Vox side chair is sure to set your venue apart from the rest. Upholstered in genuine distressed tan leather with a black steel frame the Vox hugs the shape of the user.

Held in stock for delivery in 2-3 working days. Suitable for commercial use, perfect for bars, clubs and hotels.
